#

Cream Cheese and Smoked Salmon Toast

5 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairyFish

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

Description

A quick and luxurious open-faced sandwich, perfect for breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • cream cheese: 4 oz
  • smoked salmon: 4 oz
  • capers: 1 tbsp
  • fresh dill: 1 tbsp
  • lemon juice: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
